{"tid":2072880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁愛詩：我直覺認為「特定情形」可送中審理是針對「特首犯法」","createTime":"2020-06-21T02:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T15:26:20.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"a48898183825145fa156720dcb8345b898e994f9","tid":2072880,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"草案必須寫清楚何謂「特定情形」<br />\n<br />\n被問到草案說明提到中央在「特定情形」下，對香港的國安案件有管轄權，甚至可送內地審理，梁愛詩說，由於未有看到草案條文，難以論斷，<span style=\"color: red;\">但她直覺認為，極少數情況可能會包括特首或主要官員犯法，一如以往如果港督犯法，都是由英國審理，又例如疆獨、藏獨等案件</span>，香港完全不熟悉，都可能要由中央審理。梁愛詩說，「特定情形」一定不是針對普通市民，草案條文必須要寫清楚是什麼具體情況。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國安法壓港-特定情況送中央審理-梁愛詩-須寫清楚-直覺-或包括官員犯法-疆獨藏獨/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E7%89%B9%E5%AE%9A%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%AF%A9%E7%90%86-%E6%A2%81%E6%84%9B%E8%A9%A9-%E9%A0%88%E5%AF%AB%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A-%E7%9B%B4%E8%A6%BA-%E6%88%96%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E7%8A%AF%E6%B3%95-%E7%96%86%E7%8D%A8%E8%97%8F%E7%8D%A8%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=e6e0bb4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E7%89%B9%E5%AE%9A%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%AF%A9%E7%90%86-%E6%A2%81%E6%84%9B%E8%A9%A9-%E9%A0%88%E5%AF%AB%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A-%E7%9B%B4%E8%A6%BA-%E6%88%96%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E7%8A%AF%E6%B3%95-%E7%96%86%E7%8D%A8%E8%97%8F%E7%8D%A8%2F&h=8c5da4bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國安法壓港-特定情況送中央審理-梁愛詩-須寫清楚-直覺-或包括官員犯法-疆獨藏獨/</a>"},{"pid":"a8dc2c4e403c2f04a7b37a381f362bcd139d0408","tid":2072880,"uid":100143,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:39:45.000Z","msg":"直覺...."},{"pid":"f4a6e5f88c4f94743d5edddd8d3700c3ca1f03c6","tid":2072880,"uid":108467,"like":66